snippet.title: Panic+19: Hospital Simulator | Beta Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The peak of a deadly pandemic has reached the hospital's doors, and chaos starts to take place. Are you able to save humanity from its downfall? As a doctor, welcome all critically ill patients as they arrive and attend to their needs to ensure their survival.

PLAY HERE:
https://williamjacobproductions.com/panic19

TIP: To play Multiplayer, in the Room Name, you and your friends need to enter the SAME password so that everyone can enter the same room and play together!

This is an BETA Version, this means that there's still some Unfinished Content and Bugs. In the future, Panic+19 will be fully released on Steam and Consoles!
